---

<div class="welcome-container">
  <section class="welcome-content">
    <h1>Hey there!</h1>
    <p>Welcome to my little piece of the internet.</p>
    <p>
      Most of this site is under construction so there's not much here yet, stay
      tuned for more updates!
    </p>
    <i>(or don't, y'know, whatever you wanna do is fine with me)</i>
    <p>
      Until then, here's a üçå. Also, check me out on
      <a href="https://github.com/m272cels">GitHub</a> or
      <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/m272cels">LinkedIn</a>!
    </p>
  </section>
</div>

<style>
  .welcome-container {
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: var(--color-background);
  }

  .welcome-content {
    display: flex;
    align-items: start;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 5rem 1rem;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .welcome-content h1 {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .welcome-content p,
  .welcome-content i {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .welcome-content p:not(:last-child) {
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }

  .welcome-content i {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9em;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }
  
  .welcome-content a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }
  
  .welcome-content a:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary-hover);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .welcome-content {
      padding: 10rem 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
